---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About - Hello mix">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-8 pb-12 text-lg leading-loose md:px-4">
    <h1 class="mb-12 text-4xl font-bold md:mb-8">About Hello Mix</h1>

    <h2 class="mt-10 mb-5 text-xl font-bold">A Homage to designers.mx</h2>
    <p class="mb-5">
      This website is a homage to the original <strong class="font-semibold"
        >designers.mx</strong
      >
      website. designers.mx was a beautiful platform that curated music playlists
      for designers, creating a space where creativity and sound intersected. This
      project aims to capture that same spirit and bring it back to life.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 mb-5 text-xl font-bold">Technical Details</h2>
    <p class="mb-5">
      This website is <strong class="font-semibold">open source</strong>, with
      the complete codebase accessible on GitHub:
      <a
        href="https://github.com/Utwo/hellomix"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="font-semibold text-blue-400 underline hover:text-blue-300"
        >https://github.com/Utwo/hellomix</a
      >.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-5">
      Built using modern web technologies, the site prioritizes performance,
      simplicity, and a superior user experience. Our core stack includes:
    </p>
    <ul class="my-5 list-outside list-disc">
      <li class="mb-4 pl-2">
        <strong class="font-semibold">Astro</strong> - A modern static site generator
        that delivers lightning-fast performance with minimal JavaScript
      </li>
      <li class="mb-4 pl-2">
        <strong class="font-semibold text-black dark:text-white"
          >Vanilla JavaScript</strong
        > - Clean, lightweight client-side interactions without heavy frameworks
      </li>
      <li class="mb-4 pl-2">
        <strong class="font-semibold text-black dark:text-white">CSS</strong> - Modern
        styling with responsive design and dark/light mode support
      </li>
      <li class="mb-4 pl-2">
        <strong class="font-semibold text-black dark:text-white"
          >YouTube API</strong
        > - Seamless music playback integration
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mb-5">
      The site is designed to be fast, accessible, and beautiful across all
      devices, with a focus on the music and playlists themselves.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 mb-5 text-xl font-bold">Vibe Coded</h2>
    <p class="mb-5">
      This entire website was <strong class="font-semibold">vibe coded</strong> using
      AI and music. Every line of code, every design decision, and every feature
      was crafted in a flow state, guided by AI assistance and the rhythm of the
      playlists that inspired this project.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-5">
      The result is a website that not only pays tribute to designers.mx but
      also embodies the creative energy and passion that music brings to the
      design process.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
